## Data Availability

The datasets used in this project were obtained from publicly available sources:

- GEO (Gene Expression Omnibus)
- GDSC (Genomics of Drug Sensitivity in Cancer)
- DepMap (Cancer Dependency Map)

Due to access and size constraints, the raw datasets are not included in this repository.

Users can download the datasets from:

- GEO: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/
- GDSC: https://www.cancerrxgene.org/
- DepMap: https://depmap.org/

After downloading, place the files in the `data/` directory to reproduce the analysis.
